<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Shakthi Cups | Digital Catalogue</title>

<link href="6563965-hd_1920_1080_25fps.mp4">

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
}

body{
    overflow:hidden;
}

.showcase{
    position:relative;
    width:100%;
    height:100vh;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
}

.showcase video{
    position:absolute;
    top:0;
    left:0;
    width:100%;
    height:100%;
    object-fit:cover;
}

.overlay{
    position:absolute;
    top:0;
    left:0;
    width:100%;
    height:100%;
    background:rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
}

.content{
    position:relative;
    z-index:10;
    text-align:center;
    color:white;
    max-width:900px;
    padding:20px;
}

.logo{
    font-size:4rem;
    font-weight:800;
    letter-spacing:3px;
    text-transform:uppercase;
}

.subtitle{
    font-size:1.6rem;
    margin-top:10px;
    font-weight:500;
}

.description{
    margin-top:25px;
    font-size:1.1rem;
    line-height:1.8;
}

.btn{
    display:inline-block;
    margin-top:30px;
    padding:15px 40px;
    background:white;
    color:black;
    text-decoration:none;
    border-radius:40px;
    font-weight:600;
    transition:.3s;
}

.btn:hover{
    transform:scale(1.05);
}

.products{
    position:absolute;
    bottom:40px;
    left:50%;
    transform:translateX(-50%);
    z-index:10;
    display:flex;
    gap:15px;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
    justify-content:center;
}

.product{
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
    color:white;
    padding:12px 22px;
    border-radius:30px;
    font-size:14px;
}

@media(max-width:768px){

.logo{
    font-size:2.5rem;
}

.subtitle{
    font-size:1.2rem;
}

.description{
    font-size:1rem;
}

.products{
    width:90%;
}
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<section class="showcase">

<video autoplay muted loop playsinline>
    <source src="video.mp4" type="video/mp4">
</video>

<div class="overlay"></div>

<div class="content">

<div class="logo">SHAKTHI CUPS</div>

<div class="subtitle">
India's Sustainable Packaging Partner
</div>

<div class="description">
Explore our complete range of premium Paper Cups,
Paper Bowls, CPCB Certified Compostable Bowls,
Compostable Paper Lids and Custom Printed Packaging
Solutions trusted by leading food and beverage brands.
</div>

<a href="#" class="btn">Explore Catalogue</a>

</div>

<div class="products">
<div class="product">Paper Cups</div>
<div class="product">Paper Bowls</div>
<div class="product">Compostable Bowls</div>
<div class="product">Paper Lids</div>
<div class="product">Custom Printing</div>
</div>

</section>

</body>
</html>
